{"tid":1847471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【粉嶺嘅啟示】點解唔直接封佢個關？","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:48:38.000Z","uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"122e56e6bf1208e39585e61febbb10dde96cd9d0","tid":1847471,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"搵人喺關口搞個集會，然後用炸橋起牆，各種方法封關。"},{"pid":"943c1304b29e4402861c02ebcb92d2eddd49fefc","tid":1847471,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"炸撚晒啲口岸就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8dff4e7543e73e78b090fb72941e7068429db7","tid":1847471,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23d